---
layout: base.njk
title: Core Concepts in Hindu Philosophy
description: Explore the foundational ideas of Hindu philosophy through rigorous scholarship and accessible insight.
---

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="home" class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Philosophical temple architecture with serene water reflection">
  </div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="hero-eyebrow">Philosophical Exploration</span>
    <h1>Core Concepts in Hindu Philosophy</h1>
    <p class="hero-subhead">A comprehensive journey through Vedic wisdom, metaphysical thought, and the intellectual traditions that shaped civilizations.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary">
        Explore the Book
        <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">
        Get in Touch
        <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content" data-scroll-reveal>
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>About the Author</h2>
        <p>
          This work represents decades of dedicated study, reflection, and dialogue with classical Hindu texts and contemporary scholarship. The author brings both academic rigor and genuine reverence to these timeless concepts.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rather than imposing modern frameworks onto ancient wisdom, this book allows the philosophical traditions to speak in their own voice—translated, contextualized, and made accessible to serious readers worldwide.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every chapter builds on foundational concepts, creating a pathway for readers to develop a coherent understanding of Hindu philosophy's central themes.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019418-b400bb3ab074?w=400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Author photograph" class="profile-photo">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES / BOOK DETAILS -->
<section id="services" class="section-alt-2">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-scroll-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">What's Inside</span>
      <h2>Comprehensive Exploration</h2>
      <p class="lead">Discover the three pillars of this philosophical inquiry into Hindu thought and practice.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cards">
      {% for service in services %}
      <div class="card" data-scroll-reveal>
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="{{ service.icon }}" alt="{{ service.alt }}">
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>{{ service.name }}</h3>
          <p>{{ service.description }}</p>
          <a href="#contact" class="card-link">Learn more <span>→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA SECTION -->
<section class="section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;" data-scroll-reveal>
      <h2>Begin Your Philosophical Journey</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
        Whether you're new to Hindu philosophy or deepening existing knowledge, this comprehensive work offers insight for every reader.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
        Get in Touch
        <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section id="contact" class="section-alt-2">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-scroll-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">Let's Connect</span>
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="lead">Have questions about the book or interested in speaking engagements? Reach out directly.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="contact-content">
      <div>
        <form id="contactForm" class="contact-form">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New message from Core Concepts Website">
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="align-self: flex-start;">
            Send Message
            <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
          </button>
          
          <div id="formMessage" class="form-message"></div>
        </form>
      </div>
      
      <div class="contact-info" data-scroll-reveal>
        <div class="contact-info-block">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p>For inquiries, collaborations, or speaking requests:</p>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info-block">
          <h3>Phone</h3>
          <p>Reach out directly:</p>
          <a href="tel:{{ site.phone }}">{{ site.phone_display }}</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info-block">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>Based in {{ site.address }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
